<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1915-01-04T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1915-01-04T00:00:00-05:00" n="745" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d745">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 893.773/32.</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to
                                Ambassador <persName type="to">Guthrie</persName></hi>.</head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#left">No. 90.]</seg>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>, <lb/>
                                    <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-01-04">
                                    <hi rend="italic">January 4, 1915</hi></date>.</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: Referring to the Department’s No. 81 of
                            December 8, 1914, to you, regarding the freight rate reductions
                            instituted by the South Manchuria Railway on foreign importations, there
                            is enclosed herewith for your information copy of Despatch No. 52 of
                            November 28, <pb facs="0725" n="609" xml:id="pg_609"/> 1914, from the
                            American Consul at Newchwang, with its enclosure, relating to this
                            subject.</p>
                        <p>I am [etc.]</p>
                        <closer>For the Secretary of State: <lb/>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Robert Lansing.</hi>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>